This project uses the following Arduino libraries:

- [Adafruit NeoPixel](https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit_NeoPixel) – controls the LED strip.
- [DS1302 RTC Library](https://github.com/msparks/arduino-ds1302) – handles real-time clock functions.

📦 You can install these via the Arduino Library Manager:
1. Open Arduino IDE
2. Go to **Tools > Manage Libraries...**
3. Search for “NeoPixel” and “DS1302”
4. Click “Install”
